---
import CassetteToggle from '../CassetteToggle.svelte';
---
<section class="intro">
  <h1 class="wordmark">
    Rene<CassetteToggle client:load />
  </h1>
  <div class="bio">
    <p>
      My name is Rene Ramirez. I love to tinker with technology &mdash; born in
      <span class="hl">'96</span>, the same year Nintendo dropped the N64 in Japan
      with the first analog stick anyone had ever felt. I was born in Mexico, grew up
      in the <span class="hl">SF Bay Area</span>, and live out here still.
    </p>
    <p>
      After dropping out of college I learned to program at
      <span class="hl">42</span> &mdash; a school where you teach yourself and
      amazing people from every corner of the world teach you back. From there I
      started my own IT company, got pulled into the corporate world, learned AI,
      and now we're here making amazing stuff with it.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .wordmark {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 9vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .bio {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
    display: grid; gap: 1.1rem;
  }
  .bio p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.4vw, 1.125rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hl {
    color: var(--fg);
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
